getOption(Database.DBOption) - Method in interface org.openntf.domino.ext.Database
The core lotus.domino.Database#getOption(int) method takes an int worked out by adding the integer value for all the relevant options the developer wishes to apply.

To make code clearer and easier to support, this overloaded method has been added taking a org.openntf.domino.Database.DbOption object.
